      <p class="text-[#6B7280] mb-10">I keep my focus narrow so I can do each thing well.</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="scroll-fade bg-[#EDEAE6] rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300" style="animation-delay: 0ms">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">üöÄ</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1C1C1C] mb-2">Landing Pages & Lead Capture</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#6B7280]">Fast pages that look good and actually load. Forms, CTAs, and tracking included.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="scroll-fade bg-[#EDEAE6] rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300" style="animation-delay: 80ms">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">üõ†Ô∏è</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1C1C1C] mb-2">Custom Tools & Calculators</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#6B7280]">Lead magnets, configurators, calculators. Interactive tools your audience uses, not just visits.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="scroll-fade bg-[#EDEAE6] rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300" style="animation-delay: 160ms">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">‚öôÔ∏è</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1C1C1C] mb-2">Workflow Automation</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#6B7280]">Cut the repetitive stuff. File processing, data pipelines, internal tools built to save real hours.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ‚îÄ‚îÄ ROI CALCULATOR ‚îÄ‚îÄ -->
    <section class="border-t border-[#D6D2CC] bg-[#F7F5F2]">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1C1C1C] mb-2">See What Automation Could Save You</h2>
        <p class="text-[#6B7280] mb-10">Pick the tasks eating your time. We'll show you the real cost ‚Äî and what you'd save by automating them. (Add as many as you want.)</p>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <!-- Hourly Rate Input & Add Task Button -->
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-[#D6D2CC]">
              <label for="hourlyRate" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-[#1C1C1C] mb-3">What's your hourly rate?</label>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="text-2xl text-[#6B7280]">$</span>
                <input
                  type="number"
                  id="hourlyRate"
                  value="50"
                  min="10"
                  max="500"
                  step="5"
