              <li>‚Üí Handled concurrent bidders smoothly on event night</li>
              <li>‚Üí Shipped in days, not weeks</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Project 3 -->
          <div class="scroll-fade bg-[#F7F5F2] rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300" style="animation-delay: 0ms">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-[#D97706] mb-2">Workflow Automation</p>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1C1C1C] text-lg mb-3">MP3 ID3 Tag Batch Processor</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm text-[#6B7280] space-y-2">
              <li>‚Üí Automates writing ID3 metadata tags across large audio libraries</li>
              <li>‚Üí Eliminated hours of manual file editing per batch</li>
              <li>‚Üí Custom rules engine for consistent tagging standards</li>
              <li>‚Üí Built for producers managing large back-catalog audio libraries</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Project 4 -->
          <div class="scroll-fade bg-[#F7F5F2] rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300" style="animation-delay: 80ms">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-[#D97706] mb-2">Custom Interface</p>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1C1C1C] text-lg mb-3">YouTube Competitor Interface</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm text-[#6B7280] space-y-2">
              <li>‚Üí Custom video browsing UI built on top of YouTube's API</li>
              <li>‚Üí Tailored UX for a specific content niche and audience</li>
              <li>‚Üí Strips out ads, recommendations, and noise</li>
              <li>‚Üí Shows what you can build when you're not limited by a platform</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Project 5 -->
          <div class="scroll-fade bg-[#F7F5F2] rounded-xl p-6 sm:col-span-2 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300" style="animation-delay: 40ms">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-[#D97706] mb-2">Podcast Post-Production</p>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-[#1C1C1C] text-lg mb-3">AI Workflow Automation ‚Äî Lewis Howes / School of Greatness</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm text-[#6B7280] space-y-2 sm:columns-2">
              <li>‚Üí Built AI-assisted tools to automate parts of the post-production process for School of Greatness</li>
              <li>‚Üí Cut out manual steps between recording and publish-ready files</li>
              <li>‚Üí Faster episode turnaround without adding headcount</li>
              <li>‚Üí Designed to keep up with a consistent weekly publishing schedule</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ‚îÄ‚îÄ PROCESS ‚îÄ‚îÄ -->
    <section id="process" class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1C1C1C] mb-2">How I Work</h2>
      <p class="text-[#6B7280] mb-10">Simple, fast, and collaborative.</p>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="scroll-fade text-center" style="animation-delay: 0ms">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[#D97706] text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm mb-4 mx-auto">1</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1C1C1C] mb-2">Discover</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#6B7280]">We talk through your goal, your audience, and what success actually looks like. Better to ask the hard questions up front.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="scroll-fade text-center" style="animation-delay: 100ms">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[#D97706] text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm mb-4 mx-auto">2</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1C1C1C] mb-2">Build</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#6B7280]">I build fast using AI-assisted development. You see working software early, not mockups or decks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="scroll-fade text-center" style="animation-delay: 200ms">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[#D97706] text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm mb-4 mx-auto">3</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1C1C1C] mb-2">Launch</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#6B7280]">We ship, test, and adjust. You end up with something live that you own and can maintain, not a black box.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ‚îÄ‚îÄ CONTACT ‚îÄ‚îÄ -->
    <section id="contact" class="bg-[#EDEAE6] border-t border-[#D6D2CC]">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1C1C1C] mb-2">Let's Work Together</h2>
        <p class="text-[#6B7280] mb-8">Tell me what you're building. I'll tell you if and how I can help.</p>

        <!-- Replace YOUR_FORMSPREE_ID with your actual ID from https://formspree.io -->
        <form
          action="https://formspree.io/f/xwvnnpoy"
          method="POST"
          class="space-y-5"
        >
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
            <div>
              <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-medium text-[#1C1C1C] mb-1">Your name</label>
              <input
                id="name"
                type="text"
                name="name"
                required
                placeholder="Jane Smith"
                class="w-full rounded-md border border-[#D6D2CC] bg-[#F7F5F2] px-4 py-2.5 text-sm text-[#1C1C1C] placeholder-[#9CA3AF] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#D97706]"
              />
